high_descs: Turn around and walk to the left side of the fireplace.
Pick up the pitcher on the floor.
Turn around and walk straight to the circular table.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a pitcher by the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the left side of the fireplace
Pick up the tea pot from the floor just left of the fireplace
Turn left and walk over to the small table in the corner near the chair
Turn on the table lamp that's on the table
anns.task_desc: Examine the tea pot under light of the lamp

high_descs: Turn around and move towards the fireplace then turn left and move to the area between the TV stand and the hearth.
Pick up the tea kettle on the ground.
Turn left and move past the television to the small wooden table in the corner of the room.
Turn on the lamp to the right of the credit card on the table.
anns.task_desc: Examine a tea kettle using the light from a table lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the right side of the TV stand.
Pick up the pitcher on the floor.
Turn left and go past the TV to the small wooden table in the corner of the room.
Turn on the table lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a pitcher with the illumination of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the fireplace and turn left to face the teapot on the floor.
Pick up the teapot on the floor.
Turn around to face the white couch, walk forward slightly, then turn right to cross the room, turn right at the white chair, face the small wooden table on your left and walk to it.
Turn on the lamp on the right side of the wooden table.
anns.task_desc: Examine a teapot near the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the watering can on the floor by the fireplace.
Pick up the watering can from the floor.
Turn left and walk to the lamp on the desk to the right of the chair.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a watering can by the light of a desk lamp.
